# CUSTOM Tickers & IMPROVED TRADE REVIEW

This update focuses on personalization (customizing your market watchlist) and refining the trade recording workflow by focusing on entry/exit rationale rather than generic psychological states.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **TradingView Watchlist:** You will now be able to enter a list of pairs (e.g., `BTCUSDT, ETHUSDT, SOLUSDT`) in the **Settings** tab. The dashboard ticker will automatically refresh to show your chosen coins.

> [!NOTE]
> **Rationale Focus:** Based on your request, the **Tâm lý (Psychology)** field will be removed. In its place, the exit workflow will now ask for:
> 1. **Lý do vào lệnh (Entry Reason):** To be reviewed/confirmed when closing.
> 2. **Lý do chốt lệnh (Exit Reason):** A new field to document why you decided to exit.

